ast.name: Ball Bomb
ast.comment:
Bomb has been colored as ball , your aim is to tap on the real balls as many time as possible to score the highest.
Bomb triggers off when :
(1) You tap on it
Or
(2) A Ball is not tapped for more than                    a second.

Bombs are colored red in color .

So better be quick and open your eyes to evade the bombs .
All the very best .

app.comment:

Bombs are colored red in color
Bomb triggers off when :
(1) You tap on it
Or
(2) A Ball is not tapped for more than                    a second.

(1) +3 for each tap

half a second.
